{"tid":1269633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底香港人幾時先識醒覺 點解仲要有人覺得嗌下口號就可以贏？","createTime":"2019-06-30T15:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T15:51:10.000Z","uid":267428,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3563b38580b5f362bc3cd989e168be94bbe3832f","tid":1269633,"uid":267428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"根本成場運動有616之後開始已經錯方向 開始執著要攞民意光環 恕我坦白 完全唔知有乜撚嘢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話要攞輿論壓力 迫使政府回應 係其他國家或者城市可能有作用 但在香港？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭係完全唔會理你</span></span><br />\n<br />\n經歷埋尋日死多一位烈士 <br />\n睇住一次又一次既集會一次比一次少人<br />\n甚至去到而家呢一刻熱門仲係譚詠麟啲Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚心淡<br />\n<br />\n以香港人嘅性格 死埋人咁大件事 由六九到而家已經忘記得7788<br />\n<br />\n71真係我哋最後嘅機會 過埋71我哋唔會再有任何理由號召咁多人出黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非有和理非嘅作用 但心態上一定要轉變 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n71 整體行動大綱 求咁多位勇武同和理非嚟睇一睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1265480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1265480</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n71真係我哋香港人嘅最後一場野餐<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"9146d9b2982b57ee41690f410894415a152b12dd","tid":1269633,"uid":165525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd85e3b7b59415b669998f024b41b8fdd174b88","tid":1269633,"uid":267428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:40:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf9f29940729aeff9b5266e47a04969531e728e9","tid":1269633,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:42:54.000Z","msg":"阻你少少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見到好多post話71 係去示威遊行就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位 抗爭左成個月 聽日金紫荊廣場大好機會見到政府高官 點解仲要揀去示威遊行 你地只要行出黎企出黎就幫到啲義士 唔好個個話我唔衝 無人要你衝呀 我地要人數幫啲義士cover呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我求下你地聽日朝早出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oa6Vbqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foa6Vbqx.jpg&h=7af281a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLcAVSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLcAVSd.jpg&h=67b44608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyy8wqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdyy8wqz.jpg&h=18391795&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab1820cf7752f85a331c2f166a83412d2f4a5b43","tid":1269633,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"再唔反抗，唔通人地真係驚個沙包打人咩"}]}